{"sn12.1:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 12.1 ","sn12.1:0.2":"1. Buddhavagga ","sn12.1:0.3":"Paticcasamuppadasutta ","sn12.1:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn12.1:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn12.1:1.3":"Tatra kho bhagava bhikkhu amantesi: ","sn12.1:1.4":"“bhikkhavo”ti. ","sn12.1:1.5":"“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","sn12.1:1.6":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","sn12.1:1.7":"“paticcasamuppadam vo, bhikkhave, desessami. ","sn12.1:1.8":"Tam sunatha, sadhukam manasi karotha, bhasissami”ti. ","sn12.1:1.9":"“Evam, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","sn12.1:1.10":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","sn12.1:2.1":"“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, paticcasamuppado? ","sn12.1:2.2":"Avijjapaccaya, bhikkhave, sankhara; ","sn12.1:2.3":"sankharapaccaya vinnanam; ","sn12.1:2.4":"vinnanapaccaya namarupam; ","sn12.1:2.5":"namarupapaccaya salayatanam; ","sn12.1:2.6":"salayatanapaccaya phasso; ","sn12.1:2.7":"phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.1:2.8":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn12.1:2.9":"tanhapaccaya upadanam; ","sn12.1:2.10":"upadanapaccaya bhavo; ","sn12.1:2.11":"bhavapaccaya jati; ","sn12.1:2.12":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn12.1:2.13":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn12.1:2.14":"Ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, paticcasamuppado. ","sn12.1:3.1":"Avijjaya tveva asesaviraganirodha sankharanirodho; ","sn12.1:3.2":"sankharanirodha vinnananirodho; ","sn12.1:3.3":"vinnananirodha namarupanirodho; ","sn12.1:3.4":"namarupanirodha salayatananirodho; ","sn12.1:3.5":"salayatananirodha phassanirodho; ","sn12.1:3.6":"phassanirodha vedananirodho; ","sn12.1:3.7":"vedananirodha tanhanirodho; ","sn12.1:3.8":"tanhanirodha upadananirodho; ","sn12.1:3.9":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho; ","sn12.1:3.10":"bhavanirodha jatinirodho; ","sn12.1:3.11":"jatinirodha jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa nirujjhanti. ","sn12.1:3.12":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti”ti. ","sn12.1:3.13":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","sn12.1:3.14":"Attamana te bhikkhu bhagavato bhasitam abhinandunti. ","sn12.1:3.15":"Pathamam. "}